{"tid":805239,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子在大自然的等級制度🐰🐰🌟🌟🏆🏆","createTime":"2018-09-03T15:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T15:12:22.000Z","uid":197098,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"41dd3043c880b6ede7258b3c4eef9cee2381a09a","tid":805239,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。兔子會騎着另一隻兔子背後來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。此行為是正常的，無論是雌性騎着雄性或兩隻同性別的騎着大家。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。兔子喜歡吸引人注意，有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要的，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻兔子陪伴牠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在0:59 看到：</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=b022dfa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果你在兔兔面前打開手掌，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果主人和兔兔的關係好，牠會groom主人。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說，在牠面前打開手掌是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵會放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放姿勢同驚慌一樣，但驚慌時坐姿會蹲下。) <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>以下video 是主人要求兔兔groom 主人的例子：</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=f2c06f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins>有趣視頻:</ins></em></strong></span> 兩隻兔子正在決定等級制度，但遇到困難。兔子A groom 兔子B, 但groom 了很久和等了很久還未得到回報(兔子B groom A作為回報)，所以發脾氣在2:08咬兔子B。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=996a5517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a> <br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔子的頸上來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=3dd1995b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em>N.B.</em></span>: 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會參觀然後領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=166497a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">更多資訊：</span></ins></strong><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2F&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=d6fafafb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/</a>  &amp;  <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2F&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=d8dac668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/</a>"},{"pid":"d7d2743c42c4f4ade27e799e93c0d7ede456a044","tid":805239,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"原來咁複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358da70359a6f88bf8c69da7614640593e94948e","tid":805239,"uid":175124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85728bd11e52884be96e197e88803a4798c3ae5b","tid":805239,"uid":62020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"幾得意"},{"pid":"149783ced9b8313ffe396bb3d8f1b0b3297e8215","tid":805239,"uid":69083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"幾有趣嘅智識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係兔同狼一樣 種群入面有階級觀念?"},{"pid":"bb7b082e1978cb6884cd816a7df92922763c3387","tid":805239,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"149783ced9b8313ffe396bb3d8f1b0b3297e8215","tid":805239,"uid":69083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"幾有趣嘅智識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係兔同狼一樣 種群入面有階級觀念?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"不清楚狼"},{"pid":"eae7c2567e8ba61ddb20a0288faa879dfe6b3c63","tid":805239,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f93314e63f773109818278ffd7377aa3bca9d31","tid":805239,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>不要同兔仔洗澡! 好危險!!</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n兔兔很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們有poopy butthole, 可以給牠們一個butt bath, 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>以下video 關於洗澡危險 和怎樣給牠們butt bath:</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=2c254ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔兔用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>以下視頻可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=21772782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a>"},{"pid":"b4e96efb98f296dfd09b62767875b6fefa29748a","tid":805239,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"如果佢拎個pat對住我, 我一野揸落去佢會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2b61f52acbcb9dfd205648fbc861dde0fa3b76","tid":805239,"uid":124941,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"有冇食過兔仔？<br />\n好似雞肉"},{"pid":"9305366b928779013af3100fd15980ef55b9ff76","tid":805239,"uid":174578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vf-p123yXNY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVf-p123yXNY&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=75694da5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vf-p123yXNY</a>"},{"pid":"5e606a7c03322cc69167932b9cb99b38e5cab762","tid":805239,"uid":174578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ib68DhxwUoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dib68DhxwUoQ&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=5df66cd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ib68DhxwUoQ</a>"},{"pid":"0b9fe7d5f594809d9aa04f6b804473a780705d24","tid":805239,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f93314e63f773109818278ffd7377aa3bca9d31","tid":805239,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>不要同兔仔洗澡! 好危險!!</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n兔兔很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們有poopy butthole, 可以給牠們一個butt bath, 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>以下video 關於洗澡危險 和怎樣給牠們butt bath:</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=2c254ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔兔用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>以下視頻可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=21772782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"我間中幫佢地沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a093637f1c259257c9f510b332be8e511b2172cf","tid":805239,"uid":174578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"分享幾個我follow既兔仔twitter<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/rabbit_marupii\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frabbit_marupii&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=5c8a72af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/rabbit_marupii</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://