>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_dI8437VqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg_dI8437VqM&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=6a3f000a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_dI8437VqM</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=skfym1zK4ys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dskfym1zK4ys&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=ebe28d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=skfym1zK4ys</a>"},{"pid":"8c42844e4f4f2f7731304832209b867a635a54a2","tid":805239,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>【身體語言】兔仔傷心 憂愁! +日本兔兔島&bull;大久野島!</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當兔子有一隻耳向前、一隻耳向後或一隻耳向上、一隻耳垂下，即代表牠有一點不開心或一點憤怒。但當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了。以下video 可看到牠憂愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=70008d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）很不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。<br />\n以下video 也是另一個例子，兔子生病(痙攣):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6OYkOlxe8bM&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=ca6ad51f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM</a> <br />\n<br />\n大家有沒有去過日本「兔兔島」大久野島？是兔迷必去的地方！有1000多隻自由自在地兔子活在這裡。￼<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLF7jueXt6oU&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=ab683399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU</a> <br />\n<br />\n但是其實島內的兔仔有很多活得不開心和不長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predatory animals)的威脅，但是牠們很多有生病的、沒有足夠糧食及營養。所以兔迷下次去最好帶牧草, 例如: Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等等。給牠們最基本的糧食，高纖維。不要給高糖份的和零食, 例如：蘿蔔和水果。以下video 可看到大久野島兔仔憂愁的時候:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=4cdc034f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更多關於兔子憂愁的身體語言：</span><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me%2F&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=06bdc828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/</a>"},{"pid":"47227e24a08516fdae9324e21591c27fc078aaaa","tid":805239,"uid":5375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:38:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc48d4bedcf26f7b5ca2cd820cacbf3df3f79b23","tid":805239,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>兔兔會不會發夢? 🐰</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當然會，以下videos 可看到：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發夢同主人玩：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds-7b9X5x_Ro&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=2155d9ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發夢喝水：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=2FD5muiU4IexTMhWs2%2FMYKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=94f36aab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a><br />\n<br />\n<s